'''Deb-deb''' were a sweet fruit that grew in oases on [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]] and were sometimes raided by the [[Tusken Raider/Legends|Sand People]]. They could be used to make [[Alcohol/Legends|alcoholic]] beverages.

